Crypto Ads platform

The CryptoAds Marketplace is a fully decentralized marketing platform for app publishers and advertisers, build on blockchain.
It is based on the existing project, CFC.io, which was founded back in 2012 and currently has more than 7M users worldwide as well as 100+ signed contracts with existing advertisement networks.
At CryptoAds, we offer a full range of various advertisement services, allowing to attract more traffic or monetize the existing one. You can also use our platform for tracking and reporting purposes, for both the new and the existing marketing campaigns. Finally, CryptoAds designs and supports multiple ad types, among which there are also new innovative formats like playable ads.

Why Choose Us

For Advertisers

A CryptoAds platform based on principles:

    Only one middleman inside with very low charges
    Token holders will have the power to control strategy and future development by propose features and voting process
    Each app owner will have CRAD held and platform will reward them from all transactions, depends from the amount held.
    Blockchain will provide public transparency for all transactions and marketing campaigns.
    Each mobile device will have a personal wallet, which will have a reputation rate, depends on transactions history.

For Agencies

Ours differentiates for developers/publishers:

    Storing the history of advertising offers and rewards
    Opportunity to see a full-fledged advertising campaign from various points in different agencies
    Prevention of unfair competition and underpricing of offer
    Rating of advertisers basing on the amount and accuracy of reward payouts
    Full transparent decentralized ownership, strategy and income from ecosystem growing based on active users

About us

CryptoAds platform is based on the existing project CFC.io, which was founded back in 2012 and has 7M+ users as well as more than 100 signed contracts with existing advertisement networks.

CryptoAds itself was founded in the end of 2017, and soon after the idea initiation platform development has started. In the beginning of 2019, CryptoAds opened a public access to the platform demo, so every potential customer could have a look at its functionality and decide whether it is worth his/her attention.

In less than one month after the platform demo launch CryptoAds has signed first five customers, unleashing the real potential of its invention and proving the need for such an offer on the market.

On 1st of May 2019, CryptoAds decided to expand further and launched an Initial Exchange Offering at P2PB2B. Within the next 3 days, first round of the IEO has been finished successfully, and besides the overall exposure, CryptoAds has also inspired P2PB2B with its idea, what then resulted into a partner deal.

Currently, CryptoAds accelerates its growth and looking forward to meeting new clients. Within the next 3 years, company plans to develop its own SDK for both advertisers and app publishers as well as reach more than 1M$ in revenues.

Final target will be to have $30M-$50M in revenues on a monthly basis and become a top advertisement company within the next five years.

Market of digital advertising is growing rapidly, and it is expected to have the share of 44 percent ($269.85 billion) of all ad money spent globally in 2018, with that figure reaching 50 percent ($335.48 billion) by 2020.

Considering this trend, CryptoAds designed a completely different rules of the game to provide its stakeholders with multiple opportunities that have never been offered before.

With CryptoAds, developers/publishers have a possibility of:

- Storing the history of advertising offers and rewards
- Opportunity to see a full-fledged advertising campaign from various points in different agencies
- Prevention of unfair competition and underpricing of offers
- Rating of advertisers basing on the amount and accuracy of reward payouts
- Full transparent decentralized ownership, strategy and income from ecosystem growing based on active users


End-user will benefit from:

- The history of user activity in the blockchain system
- Reward prioritization system
- The ability to offer selected priority advertising campaigns to super-users based on smart contract system
- Reputation tracking system, helping to detect and remove fraudsters

Considering all the main principles, described above, as well as current progress and overall potential, CryptoAds is the most flexible marketing platform on the market, with the unique features and numerous offers.

Still thinking? Let the technology speak for itself. Request a demo access and check it yourself!

Our story


Each companys story begins with a story of its founder. Our is not an exception. Mr. Oleksii Vynogradov, currently CEO at CryptoAds Marketplace, has always been passionate about technology and innovations. Straight after the university, Oleksii decided to deep into booming IT-industry: not only because of its obvious potential and rapid growth but rather because this was among his interests. In the age of 21, Oleksii already worked on a position of the Head of Local Representative at Odessa.net, opening a local companys office in a small city of Illichivsk (Ukraine) and establishing a wireless Internet channel between Odessa and Illichivsk. The result of his work was the first satellite Internet channel in Southeast Ukraine in a close partnership with an American company Inmarsat.
After a few years in the IT industry, Oleksii realized he has the ambition to build his own company and bring innovation to the market in his own way. In 1999, he founds IXC Softswitch, which exists up till now and is centered around developing of the wide range of contemporary information systems and technologies for communication enterprises. Portfolio of the company

constitutes of various billing systems, softswitches and system of statistics collection. IXC Softswitch was the third company worldwide, providing similar software. More than that, this company could even be found in books about the history of IP-telephony and is a benchmark of the industry.
In 2011, Oleksii founds another company, CallsFreeCalls. With his prior knowledge and experience in the field, he decides to create an app, allowing users to call anywhere in the world without paying enormous amounts of money for international calls. Basically, users had two options: either pay for the calls, either watch the ads and receive bonuses for it, using them as free minutes afterward. This app became a real breakthrough, it connected families and friends that could not pay for regular international telephone calls. With a wide network of 7M+ users, CallsFreeCalls business model attracted more and more customers, proving its validity and significance.
In 2014, Oleksii starts discovering blockchain. Long before this topic became mainstream, he adopts the technology and starts accepting cryptocurrencies as payment for calls. In the same time, CFC becomes one of the first Coinbase clients, promoting blockchain among its users. Later on, after CFC fully adopted blockchain, Oleksii decided to make a full app redesign and shift its focus from calling to earning money. After the redesign, CallsFreeCalls became Coin Fountain Club, and users got an opportunity to cash out all the money theyve been getting for ads exposures. From a free calling app, it transformed into a money generating tool, still capable of making phone calls. Each user received a personal wallet, and all the payments from that day were held in CRAD, inner CFCs currency.
However, the market continued developing, and it demonstrated a clear need for improvements. After many years of struggle with advertisement networks (providing CFCs customers with the ability to call after watching ads), Oleksii understood it could and should be changed. It often happened when these networks banned certain users and canceled payments without any reason stated, tricking its affiliates and literally stealing money from them. Support services worked in their own preferred way, supplying affiliates with intentionally wrong information, all the disputes lasted for weeks and months, and at the certain period of time, Oleksii said to himself: this is the last straw.
Based on his painful experience, at the end of 2017, Oleksii decided to gather a team of like-minded professionals and start building the new generation of advertising platforms, with a clear structure, transparent interaction and fast transactions within the ecosystem. Already in 2019, the platform has been launched and the first clients got an opportunity to try it out. The general feedback was very positive, and even the platform is still very young, it has already signed a few big advertisement networks.
CryptoAds has a really unique concept behind. Besides the security and transparency blockchain provides, CryptoAds is very different from existing analogs due to its flexibility of monetization types. Market changes and CryptoAds want to form the new customer journey. With CryptoAds, there is no need to search for the advertising network that supports your desired ad format. Just state which one is preferred and test it! Also, CryptoAds does not support the vertical structure of the relationship with customers, which remains common until now instead, it chooses horizontal and encourages existing users to vote for features/improvements they want. You may think you know what people want, but it is smarter to just ask them.
Now, after multiple obstacles and challenges on his way, Oleksii drives innovations forward, redefining the AdTech industry and setting up the new rules of the game. Years will pass, but CryptoAds will remain the big name in digital advertising history as the first decentralized blockchain marketing platform in the world, built for its users benefit.
